data.description: Completely renovated 4bed/2bath home on double lot in Van Buren! Located in the heart of town, this home features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and neutral paint throughout. Upstairs includes 3bedrooms, 1 full bath, kitchen and dining. Downstairs you will find the master suite with an oversized walk-in closet and full bath. Call today for your showing!
